To run the BTA.

1. Start ciao
2.  use_module(autobta).
3.  ?- test.
4.  Look at output in the files with .bta extension in Tests/
5.  See autobta.pl file for examples of how to run the analysis.



To compile the auto_bta for use with logen:

[wlan-155:~/asap_cvs_root/Systems/bta] mal% ciaoc auto_bta                     
 ==> generates the auto_bta executable
 
[wlan-155:~/asap_cvs_root/Systems/bta] mal% ./auto_bta ~/cvs_root/cogen2/examples/match.pl.ann logen/logenbta.pl ~/out
 :- filter static\==dynamic.
 :- filter match1(static,dynamic,static,dynamic).
 :- filter match(static,dynamic).

To run the script call:
python convert.py CIAO
or 
python convert.py SICS

which will convert all source to either CIAO mode or SICSTUS mode.

